CANAVERAL INTERNATIONAL CORPORATION and Bimini Run, Ltd., Appellant, v. TALCO CAPITAL CORPORATION, Appellee. No. 21582. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. May 10, 1965. Robert H. Givens, Jr., Dubbin, Schiff, Berkman & Dubbin, Miami, Fla., for appellants. Richard P. Kenney, Williams, Salomon & Kenney, Miami, Fla., for appellee.

Before TUTTLE, Chief Judge, BELL, Circuit Judge, and DYER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM:

The opinion of the District Court in 225 F.Supp. 1007 is correct and the judgment is

Affirmed.
